1. Morao sam *prekinuti* razgovor zbog važnog sastanka. (I had to *interrupt* the conversation because of an important meeting.)
2. Uspjeli su *prekinuti* napad terorista. (They managed to *prevent* the terrorist attack.)
3. Nadam se da će kiša *prekinuti* uskoro. (I hope that the rain will *stop* soon.)
4. Moramo *prekinuti* sa ovim lošim navikama. (We need to *break* these bad habits.)
5. *Prekinuli* smo saradnju sa tom kompanijom. (We *terminated* cooperation with that company.)
6. Ukoliko želite, možemo *prekinuti* sastanak ranije. (If you wish, we can *end* the meeting earlier.)
7. Njihov dogovor je *prekinut* zbog nesuglasica. (Their agreement was *disrupted* due to disagreements.)
8. Niko ne smije *prekinuti* tišinu u biblioteci. (No one is allowed to *disturb* the silence in the library.)
9. Njihov razgovor je *prekinut* dolaskom gostiju. (Their conversation was *interrupted* by the arrival of guests.)
10. Čekali smo da se veza *prekine* kako bismo pozvali tehničku podršku. (We waited for the connection to *break* so that we could call technical support.)